The '''Five Star Movement''' ({{lang-it|Movimento 5 Stelle}} {{IPA-it|moviˈmento ˈtʃiŋkwe ˈstelle|}}, '''M5S''') is a [[List of political parties in Italy|political party in Italy]]. The M5S was founded on 4 October 2009 by [[Beppe Grillo]], a popular comedian and blogger, and [[Gianroberto Casaleggio]], a [[Web strategy|web strategist]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Notizie in due minuti|url=http://archiviostorico.corriere.it/2009/ottobre/05/NOTIZIE_DUE_MINUTI_co_9_091005092.shtml|work=Corriere della Sera|accessdate=27 May 2012|page=64|date=5 October 2009}}</ref> After Casaleggio's death in April 2016, Grillo appointed a directorate composed of five leading MPs (Alessandro Di Battista, [[Luigi Di Maio]], [[Roberto Fico]], Carla Ruocco and Carlo Sibilia),<ref>This party structure had no official name, but it was quickly nicknamed the ''Direttorio'' ("Directorate") by the Italian press. [http://www.ansa.it/english/news/2014/11/28/m5s-supporters-give-thumbs-up-to-grillo-directorate_36728cc6-397b-4138-b39e-971aa1ef521d.html "M5S supporters give thumbs up to Grillo directorate"] and [http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/politica/2014/11/28/m5s-grillo-sono-stanchino.-propone-collegio-di-garanti_ae6cfa21-ae9b-4e68-bf51-0f7e8ee0486d.html "Grillo è 'stanchino', nomina direttorio. Partito insorge"] (28 novembre 2014). ANSA. Retrieved 4 June 2018.</ref> which lasted until the following October when he dissolved it and proclaimed himself the "political head" of the M5S.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ilsole24ore.com/art/notizie/2016-09-25/svolta-grillo-sono-capo-politico-104900.shtml?uuid=ADHlZaQB|title=Svolta di Grillo: "Sono il capo politico"|work=Il Sole 24 Ore}}</ref> Grillo is also formally president of the association named the Five Star Movement; his nephew, Enrico Grillo, serves as vice president; and his accountant, Enrico Maria Nadasi, as secretary.<ref name="M5S"/> [[Davide Casaleggio]], Gianroberto's son, has an increasingly important albeit unofficial role.<ref>{{cite web|author=Di martedì 19 aprile 2016|url=http://www.polisblog.it/post/373565/chi-comanda-ora-nel-movimento-5-stelle-il-ruolo-di-davide-casaleggio|title=Chi comanda ora nel Movimento 5 Stelle? Il ruolo di Davide Casaleggio|publisher=Polisblog|date=19 April 2016|accessdate=18 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Altri articoli dalla categoria|url=http://www.repubblica.it/politica/2016/09/21/news/davide_casaleggio_m5s-148271023/|title=M5s, la prima volta di Davide Casaleggio|work=la Repubblica|date=21 September 2016|accessdate=18 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nextquotidiano.it/nuovo-regolamento-m5s-casaleggio-espulsioni/|title=Il nuovo regolamento M5S e il ruolo di Davide Casaleggio nelle espulsioni|publisher=neXtQuotidiano|date=26 September 2016|accessdate=18 April 2017}}</ref>

